        "action": "Increase funding for those chiidren  with SEN when school resumes.",
        "additional_details": "During this period of lockdown many  children who have SEN  will not be able to access their support contained in their EHCP\r\nBeing home schooled  is particularly challenging  for those  children. \r\nMany  may struggles to write, understand language and  process information. They will struggle to re establish routines and the ability to socialise.\r\nDuring the period,they might  fall further behind their peers. Many would  having started this period a few years  academically behind their peers.",
        "background": "The Government needs to provide schools with additional ring fenced funding for those children who would normally qualify for Top Up or Low incident / high needs funding.",
